48 (a) A release of, or addition to, property encumbered by a mortgage;
49 (b) A release of, addition of, or other change in an obligor; or
50 (c) An assignment or other transfer of a mortgage or an obligation.
51 Sec. 48. 1. For a mortgage modification described in subsection 2:
52 (a) The mortgage continues to secure the obligation as modified;
53 (b) The priority of the mortgage is not affected by the modification;

